name: Humerus Bone Earring - Triple Steel Long
description:
Perfect for people that love biology or want something unique to your own style. These anatomically correct humerus bones are 3d printed cutlery grade grade steel with infused phosphor bronze. The length is of each bone is 3.5cm (1.38in). Total length of the earring dangling is 8.7cm (3.42in).

Designer, Sculptor, Assembling Drone: Kris Rekers.

Model: Brandi Taylor

All stages from prototype to finish were hand crafted. This toy is hand cast in plastic for a small limited run.
